  "title": "ACCOUNTS & ADMIN EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Assist in daily finance operations (includes payments, receipts, AP & AR transactions);-</li><li>Assist in partial/full set of accounts and prepare balance sheet schedules and ensure timely, complete and accurate recording of accounting entries into MYOB accounting system;</li><li>Posting of month-end closing journal entries;</li><li>General office administration such as: filing, scanning, photocopying, archiving, office supplies;</li><li>Assist in preparing documents for submission of government grant claims;</li><li>Manage and handle documents, records and maintain an organized filing system.</li><li>Any other ad hoc duties as assigned by Manager in-charge</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>LCCI or Diploma in Accounting</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Excel and Word</li><li>Fast learner with strong sense of initiative & good communication skills- Able to work independently with minimum supervision</li></ul>",
